  "title": "The Most Inspiring Speech: The Wisdom of a Third Grade Dropout Will Change Your Life | Rick Rigsby",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 165.0,
      "end_time": 3254.0,
      "text": "- The wisest person I ever met in my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3254.0,
      "end_time": 5087.0,
      "text": "a third grade dropout."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 6114.0,
      "end_time": 8211.0,
      "text": "Wisest and dropout in the same sentence"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8211.0,
      "end_time": 9666.0,
      "text": "is rather oxymoronic"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 9666.0,
      "end_time": 10797.0,
      "text": "like jumbo shrimp."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 10797.0,
      "end_time": 13061.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 13061.0,
      "end_time": 13896.0,
      "text": "Mhmm."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 13896.0,
      "end_time": 15969.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 15969.0,
      "end_time": 17285.0,
      "text": "Like fun run."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 17285.0,
      "end_time": 18472.0,
      "text": "Ain't nothing fun about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 18472.0,
      "end_time": 20645.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 20645.0,
      "end_time": 24010.0,
      "text": "Like Microsoft Works, y'all don't hear me."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 24010.0,
      "end_time": 25769.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 25769.0,
      "end_time": 27747.0,
      "text": "I used to say I like country music"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 27747.0,
      "end_time": 29623.0,
      "text": "but I've lived in Texas so long"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 29623.0,
      "end_time": 31245.0,
      "text": "I love country music now."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 31245.0,
      "end_time": 32645.0,
      "text": "(audience cheering)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 32645.000000000004,
      "end_time": 33870.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 33870.0,
      "end_time": 37462.0,
      "text": "I hunt, I fish, I have\ncowboy boots, and cowboy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 37462.0,
      "end_time": 38960.0,
      "text": "y'all, I'm a black neck redneck."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 38960.0,
      "end_time": 41181.0,
      "text": "Do you hear what I'm saying to you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 41181.0,
      "end_time": 42789.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 42789.0,
      "end_time": 46266.0,
      "text": "No longer oxymoronic for\nme to say country music."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 46266.0,
      "end_time": 48074.0,
      "text": "And it's not oxymoronic for me to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 48074.0,
      "end_time": 50436.0,
      "text": "third grade and dropout."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 50436.0,
      "end_time": 51399.0,
      "text": "That third grade dropout,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 51399.0,
      "end_time": 53304.0,
      "text": "the wisest person I ever met in my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 53304.0,
      "end_time": 57478.0,
      "text": "who taught me to combine\nknowledge and wisdom"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 57478.0,
      "end_time": 59010.0,
      "text": "to make an impact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 59010.0,
      "end_time": 60461.0,
      "text": "was my father."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 60461.0,
      "end_time": 61628.0,
      "text": "A simple cook."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 62511.0,
      "end_time": 64974.0,
      "text": "Wisest man I ever met in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 64974.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66571.0,
      "text": "Just a simple cook."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 66571.0,
      "end_time": 67722.0,
      "text": "Left school in the third grade"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 67722.0,
      "end_time": 68989.0,
      "text": "to help out on the family farm"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 68989.0,
      "end_time": 70450.0,
      "text": "but just because he left school"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 70450.0,
      "end_time": 72759.0,
      "text": "doesn't mean education stopped."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 72759.0,
      "end_time": 73662.0,
      "text": "Mark Twain once said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 73662.0,
      "end_time": 74622.0,
      "text": "\"I've never allowed my schooling"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 74622.0,
      "end_time": 76950.0,
      "text": "\"to get in the way of my education.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 76950.0,
      "end_time": 78440.0,
      "text": "My father taught himself how to read,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 78440.0,
      "end_time": 79920.0,
      "text": "taught himself how to write."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 79920.0,
      "end_time": 82056.0,
      "text": "Decided in the midst of Jim Crowism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 82056.0,
      "end_time": 85264.0,
      "text": "as America was breathing the\nlast gasp of the Civil War,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 85264.0,
      "end_time": 88303.0,
      "text": "my father decided he was\ngonna stand and be a man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 88303.0,
      "end_time": 90006.0,
      "text": "not a black man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 90006.0,
      "end_time": 92066.0,
      "text": "not a brown man, not a white man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 92066.0,
      "end_time": 92899.0,
      "text": "but a man."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 94028.0,
      "end_time": 98924.0,
      "text": "He literally challenged himself\nto be the best that he could"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 98924.0,
      "end_time": 101508.0,
      "text": "all the days of his life."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 101508.0,
      "end_time": 103104.0,
      "text": "I have four degrees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 103104.0,
      "end_time": 105330.0,
      "text": "my brother is a judge."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 105330.0,
      "end_time": 107842.0,
      "text": "We're not the smartest ones in our family."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 107842.0,
      "end_time": 110179.0,
      "text": "It's a third grade dropout daddy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 110179.0,
      "end_time": 112115.0,
      "text": "a third grade dropout daddy"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 112115.0,
      "end_time": 114054.0,
      "text": "who was quoting\nMichelangelo, saying to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 114054.0,
      "end_time": 116816.0,
      "text": "\"Boys, I won't have a problem\nif you aim high and miss"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 116816.0,
      "end_time": 117996.0,
      "text": "\"but I'm gonna have a real issue"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 117996.0,
      "end_time": 120266.0,
      "text": "\"if you aim low and hit.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 120266.0,
      "end_time": 123399.0,
      "text": "A country mother quoting\nHenry Ford, saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 123399.0,
      "end_time": 125745.0,
      "text": "\"If you think you can or\nif you think you can't,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 125745.0,
      "end_time": 126767.0,
      "text": "\"you're right.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 126767.0,
      "end_time": 129952.0,
      "text": "I learned that from a third\ngrade drop, simple lessons."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 129952.0,
      "end_time": 130854.0,
      "text": "Lessons like these."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 130854.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132786.0,
      "text": "\"Son, you'd rather be an hour early"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 132786.0,
      "end_time": 134177.0,
      "text": "\"than a minute late.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 134177.0,
      "end_time": 135489.0,
      "text": "We never knew what time it was at my house"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 135489.0,
      "end_time": 137389.0,
      "text": "'cause the clocks were always ahead."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 137389.0,
      "end_time": 139216.0,
      "text": "My mother said for nearly 30 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 139216.0,
      "end_time": 141729.0,
      "text": "my father left the house\nat 3:45 in the morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 141729.0,
      "end_time": 143308.0,
      "text": "One day she asked him, \"Why, Daddy?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 143308.0,
      "end_time": 144824.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Maybe one of my boys"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 144824.0,
      "end_time": 146720.0,
      "text": "\"will catch me in the act of excellence.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 146720.0,
      "end_time": 148249.0,
      "text": "I wanna share two things with you."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 148249.0,
      "end_time": 150770.0,
      "text": "Aristotle said you are\nwhat you repeatedly do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 150770.0,
      "end_time": 154319.0,
      "text": "therefore excellence ought\nto be a habit not an act."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 154319.0,
      "end_time": 155883.0,
      "text": "Don't ever forget that."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 155883.0,
      "end_time": 158733.0,
      "text": "I know you're tough but\nalways remember to be kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 158733.0,
      "end_time": 159567.0,
      "text": "Always."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 159567.0,
      "end_time": 161159.0,
      "text": "Don't ever forget that."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 161159.0,
      "end_time": 163439.0,
      "text": "Never embarrass momma."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 163439.0,
      "end_time": 164272.0,
      "text": "Mhmm."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 164272.0,
      "end_time": 165371.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 165371.0,
      "end_time": 168517.0,
      "text": "Yeah, if momma ain't\nhappy, ain't nobody happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 168517.0,
      "end_time": 170599.0,
      "text": "If daddy ain't happy, don't\nnobody care but you know--"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 170599.0,
      "end_time": 171432.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 171432.0,
      "end_time": 172349.0,
      "text": "I tell you."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 173289.0,
      "end_time": 174289.0,
      "text": "Next lesson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 175238.0,
      "end_time": 178490.0,
      "text": "lesson from a cook over\nthere in the galley."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 178490.0,
      "end_time": 180340.0,
      "text": "Son, make sure your servant's towel"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 180340.0,
      "end_time": 182064.0,
      "text": "is bigger than your ego."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 182064.0,
      "end_time": 187038.0,
      "text": "Ego is the anesthesia that\ndeadens the pain of stupidity."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 187038.0,
      "end_time": 188913.0,
      "text": "Y'all might have a relative in mind"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 188913.0,
      "end_time": 189746.0,
      "text": "you wanna send that to."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 189746.0,
      "end_time": 190647.0,
      "text": "Let me say it again."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 190647.0,
      "end_time": 192272.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 192272.0,
      "end_time": 195441.0,
      "text": "Ego is the anesthesia that\ndeadens the pain of stupidity."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 195441.0,
      "end_time": 197063.0,
      "text": "Pride is the burden of a foolish person."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 197063.0,
      "end_time": 200394.0,
      "text": "John Wooden coached basketball\nin UCLA for a living"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 200394.0,
      "end_time": 202531.0,
      "text": "but his calling was to impact people."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 202531.0,
      "end_time": 204683.0,
      "text": "And with all those national championships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 204683.0,
      "end_time": 207194.0,
      "text": "guess what he was found doing\nin the middle of the week?"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 207194.0,
      "end_time": 208171.0,
      "text": "Going into the cupboard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 208171.0,
      "end_time": 212426.0,
      "text": "grabbing a broom and\nsweeping his own gym floor."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 212426.0,
      "end_time": 214310.0,
      "text": "You wanna make an impact?"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 214310.0,
      "end_time": 215700.0,
      "text": "Find your broom."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 215700.0,
      "end_time": 217665.0,
      "text": "Every day of your life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 217665.0,
      "end_time": 218768.0,
      "text": "you find your broom."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 218768.0,
      "end_time": 221060.0,
      "text": "You grow your influence that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 221060.0,
      "end_time": 222850.0,
      "text": "That way you're attracting people"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 222850.0,
      "end_time": 224888.0,
      "text": "so that you can impact them."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 224888.0,
      "end_time": 226457.0,
      "text": "Final lesson."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 226457.0,
      "end_time": 227290.0,
      "text": "\"Son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 229258.0,
      "end_time": 231442.0,
      "text": "\"you're gonna do a job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 231442.0,
      "end_time": 232609.0,
      "text": "\"do it right.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 233775.0,
      "end_time": 235525.0,
      "text": "I've always been told"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 236526.0,
      "end_time": 238276.0,
      "text": "how average I can be."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 239952.0,
      "end_time": 243204.0,
      "text": "Always been criticized about being average"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 243204.0,
      "end_time": 244948.0,
      "text": "but I wanna tell you something."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 244948.0,
      "end_time": 246863.0,
      "text": "I stand here before you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 246863.0,
      "end_time": 248489.0,
      "text": "before all of these people"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 248489.0,
      "end_time": 250942.0,
      "text": "not listening to those words"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 250942.0,
      "end_time": 253916.0,
      "text": "but telling myself every single day"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 253916.0,
      "end_time": 255710.0,
      "text": "to shoot for the stars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 255710.0,
      "end_time": 257869.0,
      "text": "to be the best that I can be."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 257869.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259106.00000000003,
      "text": "Good enough isn't good enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 259106.0,
      "end_time": 260333.0,
      "text": "if it can be better."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 260333.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261608.00000000003,
      "text": "And better isn't good enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 261608.0,
      "end_time": 263311.0,
      "text": "if it can be best."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 263311.0,
      "end_time": 265790.0,
      "text": "Let me close with a very personal story"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 265790.0,
      "end_time": 268396.0,
      "text": "that I think will bring\nall this into focus."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 268396.0,
      "end_time": 271642.0,
      "text": "Wisdom will come to you in\nthe unlikeliest of sources."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 271642.0,
      "end_time": 273321.0,
      "text": "A lot of times through failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 273321.0,
      "end_time": 275762.0,
      "text": "When you hit rock bottom remember this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 275762.0,
      "end_time": 277362.0,
      "text": "while you're struggling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 277362.0,
      "end_time": 279707.0,
      "text": "rock bottom can also be a great foundation"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 279707.0,
      "end_time": 280947.0,
      "text": "on which to build"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 280947.0,
      "end_time": 282430.0,
      "text": "and on which to grow."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 282430.0,
      "end_time": 285187.0,
      "text": "I'm not worried that you'll be successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 285187.0,
      "end_time": 289157.0,
      "text": "I'm worried that you won't\nfail from time to time."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 289157.0,
      "end_time": 292848.0,
      "text": "A person that gets up off\nthe canvas and keeps growing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 292848.0,
      "end_time": 293762.0,
      "text": "that's the person"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 293762.0,
      "end_time": 296617.0,
      "text": "that will continue to\ngrow their influence."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 296617.0,
      "end_time": 298129.0,
      "text": "Back in the '70s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 298129.0,
      "end_time": 300562.0,
      "text": "to help me make this point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 300562.0,
      "end_time": 302618.0,
      "text": "let me introduce you to someone."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 302618.0,
      "end_time": 305881.0,
      "text": "I met the finest woman\nI'd ever met in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 305881.0,
      "end_time": 306714.0,
      "text": "Mhmm."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 306714.0,
      "end_time": 307898.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 307898.0,
      "end_time": 311206.0,
      "text": "Back in my day, we'd have\ncalled her a brick house."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 311206.0,
      "end_time": 314839.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 314839.0,
      "end_time": 316952.0,
      "text": "This woman was the finest\nwoman I'd ever seen in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 316952.0,
      "end_time": 318276.0,
      "text": "There's just one little problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 318276.0,
      "end_time": 321571.0,
      "text": "Back then ladies didn't\nlike big old line men."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 321571.0,
      "end_time": 323094.0,
      "text": "The Blindside hadn't come out yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 323094.0,
      "end_time": 325391.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 325391.0,
      "end_time": 327383.0,
      "text": "They liked quarterbacks and running backs."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 327383.0,
      "end_time": 328216.0,
      "text": "We're at this dance"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 328216.0,
      "end_time": 330557.0,
      "text": "and I find out her name is Trina Williams"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 330557.0,
      "end_time": 332103.0,
      "text": "from Lompoc, California"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 332103.0,
      "end_time": 333595.0,
      "text": "and we were all dancing"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 333595.0,
      "end_time": 335760.0,
      "text": "and we're just excited"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 335760.0,
      "end_time": 337630.0,
      "text": "and I decide in the\nmiddle of dancing with her"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 337630.0,
      "end_time": 339438.0,
      "text": "that I would ask her for her phone number."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 339438.0,
      "end_time": 341339.0,
      "text": "She, Trina was the first one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 341339.0,
      "end_time": 342898.0,
      "text": "Trina was the only woman in college"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 342898.0,
      "end_time": 344597.0,
      "text": "who gave me her real telephone number."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 344597.0,
      "end_time": 346177.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 346177.0,
      "end_time": 348541.0,
      "text": "The next day we walked\nto Baskin and Robbins"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 348541.0,
      "end_time": 349945.0,
      "text": "ice cream parlor."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 349945.0,
      "end_time": 351538.0,
      "text": "My friends couldn't believe it."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 351538.0,
      "end_time": 353476.0,
      "text": "This has been 40 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 353476.0,
      "end_time": 355130.0,
      "text": "and my friends still can't believe it."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 355130.0,
      "end_time": 356263.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 356263.0,
      "end_time": 358105.0,
      "text": "We go on a second date"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 358105.0,
      "end_time": 360011.0,
      "text": "and a third date"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 360011.0,
      "end_time": 362075.0,
      "text": "and a fourth date."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 362075.0,
      "end_time": 362908.0,
      "text": "Mhmm."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 362908.0,
      "end_time": 364354.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 364354.0,
      "end_time": 366688.0,
      "text": "We drive from Chico to Vallejo"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 366688.0,
      "end_time": 368529.0,
      "text": "so that she could meet my parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 368529.0,
      "end_time": 369911.0,
      "text": "My father meets her."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 369911.0,
      "end_time": 372762.0,
      "text": "My daddy, my hero, he meets her,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 372762.0,
      "end_time": 375268.0,
      "text": "pulls me to the side and\nsays, \"Is she psycho?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 375268.0,
      "end_time": 376101.0,
      "text": "But anyway--"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 376101.0,
      "end_time": 377471.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 377471.0,
      "end_time": 378995.0,
      "text": "We go together for a year, two years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 378995.0,
      "end_time": 380086.0,
      "text": "three years, four years"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 380086.0,
      "end_time": 382004.0,
      "text": "by now Trina's a senior in college."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 382004.0,
      "end_time": 382995.0,
      "text": "I'm still a freshman"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 382995.0,
      "end_time": 384812.0,
      "text": "but I'm working some things out."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 384812.0,
      "end_time": 386691.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 386691.0,
      "end_time": 389351.0,
      "text": "I'm so glad I graduated in four terms."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 389351.0,
      "end_time": 391292.0,
      "text": "Nixon, Ford, Carter, Reagan."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 391292.0,
      "end_time": 393713.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 393713.0,
      "end_time": 395805.0,
      "text": "So now it's time to propose."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 395805.0,
      "end_time": 397636.0,
      "text": "So I talked to her girlfriends"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 397636.0,
      "end_time": 399237.0,
      "text": "and it's California, it's in the '70s."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 399237.0,
      "end_time": 400375.0,
      "text": "So it has to be outside,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 400375.0,
      "end_time": 402890.0,
      "text": "have to have a candle\nand you have to have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 402890.0,
      "end_time": 403993.0,
      "text": "some chocolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 403993.0,
      "end_time": 404826.0,
      "text": "Listen, I'm from the hood."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 404826.0,
      "end_time": 406703.0,
      "text": "I had a bottle of Boone's Farm wine."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 406703.0,
      "end_time": 407536.0,
      "text": "That's what I had."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 407536.0,
      "end_time": 408777.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 408777.0,
      "end_time": 409860.0,
      "text": "She said yes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 411113.0,
      "end_time": 412497.0,
      "text": "That was the key."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 412497.0,
      "end_time": 413746.0,
      "text": "I married the most beautiful woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 413746.0,
      "end_time": 415070.0,
      "text": "I'd ever seen in my--"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 415070.0,
      "end_time": 416129.0,
      "text": "'all ever been to a wedding"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 416129.0,
      "end_time": 418499.0,
      "text": "and even before the wedding\nstarts you hear this."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 418499.0,
      "end_time": 420199.0,
      "text": "\"How in the world?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 420199.0,
      "end_time": 423470.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 423470.0,
      "end_time": 426456.0,
      "text": "And it was coming from\nmy side of the family!"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 426456.0,
      "end_time": 429456.0,
      "text": "(audience laughing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 431165.0,
      "end_time": 433511.0,
      "text": "We get married, we have a few children."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 433511.0,
      "end_time": 435555.0,
      "text": "Our lives are great."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 435555.0,
      "end_time": 439223.0,
      "text": "One day Trina finds a\nlump in her left breast."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 439223.0,
      "end_time": 440999.0,
      "text": "Breast cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 440999.0,
      "end_time": 443612.0,
      "text": "Six years after that diagnosis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 443612.0,
      "end_time": 448375.0,
      "text": "me and my two little boys\nwalked up to mommy's casket"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 448375.0,
      "end_time": 450973.0,
      "text": "and for two years my heart didn't beat."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 450973.0,
      "end_time": 452685.0,
      "text": "If it wasn't for my faith in God"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 452685.0,
      "end_time": 454350.0,
      "text": "I wouldn't be standing here today."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 454350.0,
      "end_time": 456753.0,
      "text": "If it wasn't for those two little boys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 456753.0,
      "end_time": 460476.0,
      "text": "there'd have been no\nreason for which to go on."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 460476.0,
      "end_time": 462309.0,
      "text": "I was completely lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 464034.0,
      "end_time": 465784.0,
      "text": "That was rock bottom."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 466873.0,
      "end_time": 468874.0,
      "text": "You know what sustained me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 468874.0,
      "end_time": 471696.0,
      "text": "The wisdom of a third grade dropout."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 471696.0,
      "end_time": 474029.0,
      "text": "The wisdom of a simple cook."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 474922.0,
      "end_time": 476236.0,
      "text": "We're at the casket."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 476236.0,
      "end_time": 478418.0,
      "text": "I'd never seen my dad cry"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 478418.0,
      "end_time": 479852.0,
      "text": "but this time I saw my dad cry."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 479852.0,
      "end_time": 480810.0,
      "text": "That was his daughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 480810.0,
      "end_time": 482230.0,
      "text": "Trina was his daughter"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 482230.0,
      "end_time": 483751.0,
      "text": "not his daughter-in-law."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 483751.0,
      "end_time": 485121.0,
      "text": "And I'm right behind my father"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 485121.0,
      "end_time": 488002.0,
      "text": "about to see her for the\nlast time on this earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 488002.0,
      "end_time": 489771.0,
      "text": "and my father shared three words with me"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 489771.0,
      "end_time": 492581.0,
      "text": "that changed my life\nright there at the casket."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 492581.0,
      "end_time": 495483.0,
      "text": "It would be the last lesson\nhe would ever teach me."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 495483.0,
      "end_time": 496650.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 497664.0,
      "end_time": 498664.0,
      "text": "\"just stand."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 499941.0,
      "end_time": 502084.0,
      "text": "\"You keep standing."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 502084.0,
      "end_time": 502917.0,
      "text": "\"You keep standing."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 502917.0,
      "end_time": 504986.0,
      "text": "\"No matter how rough the\nsea, you keep standing."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 504986.0,
      "end_time": 507225.0,
      "text": "\"And I'm not talking about just water."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 507225.0,
      "end_time": 509020.0,
      "text": "\"You keep standing."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 509020.0,
      "end_time": 512063.0,
      "text": "\"No matter what, you don't give up.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 512063.0,
      "end_time": 515557.0,
      "text": "And as clearly as I'm\ntalking to you today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 515557.0,
      "end_time": 518346.0,
      "text": "these were some of her last words to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 518346.0,
      "end_time": 520987.0,
      "text": "She looked me in the eye and she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 520986.99999999994,
      "end_time": 524354.0,
      "text": "\"It doesn't matter to me\nany longer how long I live."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 524354.0,
      "end_time": 526269.0,
      "text": "\"What matters to me most"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 526269.0,
      "end_time": 528199.0,
      "text": "\"is how I live.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 528199.0,
      "end_time": 530164.0,
      "text": "I ask you all one question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 530164.0,
      "end_time": 532261.0,
      "text": "a question that I was asked all my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 532261.0,
      "end_time": 534419.0,
      "text": "by a third grade dropout."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 534419.0,
      "end_time": 536353.0,
      "text": "\"How you livin'?"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 536353.0,
      "end_time": 537376.0,
      "text": "\"How you livin'?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 537376.0,
      "end_time": 539539.0,
      "text": "Everyday ask yourself that question."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 539539.0,
      "end_time": 540675.0,
      "text": "How you livin'?"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 540675.0,
      "end_time": 544638.0,
      "text": "Here's, here's what a cook would suggest"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 544638.0,
      "end_time": 546839.0,
      "text": "you to live, this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 546839.0,
      "end_time": 548481.0,
      "text": "That you would not judge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 548481.0,
      "end_time": 550734.0,
      "text": "that you would show up early,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 550734.0,
      "end_time": 552372.0,
      "text": "that you'd be kind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 552372.0,
      "end_time": 555497.0,
      "text": "that you'd make sure\nthat that servant's towel"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 555497.0,
      "end_time": 556748.0,
      "text": "is huge and used,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 556748.0,
      "end_time": 558391.0,
      "text": "that if you're gonna do something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 558391.0,
      "end_time": 560141.0,
      "text": "you do it the right way."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 560141.0,
      "end_time": 562506.0,
      "text": "That cook would tell you this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 562506.0,
      "end_time": 564828.0,
      "text": "that it's never wrong\nto do the right thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 564828.0,
      "end_time": 566576.0,
      "text": "that how you do anything"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 566576.0,
      "end_time": 568520.0,
      "text": "is how you do everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 568520.0,
      "end_time": 570569.0,
      "text": "And in that way you\nwill grow your influence"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 570569.0,
      "end_time": 571928.0,
      "text": "to make an impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 571928.0,
      "end_time": 573384.0,
      "text": "In that way you will honor all those"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 573384.0,
      "end_time": 574728.0,
      "text": "who have gone before you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 574728.0,
      "end_time": 575971.0,
      "text": "who have invested in you."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 575971.0,
      "end_time": 579101.0,
      "text": "Look in those unlikeliest\nplaces for wisdom."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 579101.0,
      "end_time": 583344.0,
      "text": "Enhance your life every\nday by seeking that wisdom"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 583344.0,
      "end_time": 585825.0,
      "text": "and asking yourself every night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 585825.0,
      "end_time": 587111.0,
      "text": "\"How am I living?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 587111.0,
      "end_time": 588438.0,
      "text": "May God richly bless you all."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 588438.0,
      "end_time": 589898.0,
      "text": "Thank you for having me."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 589898.0,
      "end_time": 594090.0,
      "text": "(audience cheering and applauding)"
